      <button
        type="submit"
        class="w-full py-4 mt-2 bg-linear-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-400 text-white font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-200/50 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm"
      >
        Enviar Confirmaci칩n
